{"tid":562951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"初一到初三泊車唔抄牌","createTime":"2018-02-16T11:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T12:30:25.000Z","uid":108756,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ece9da60c6434f55a77952b3802dddfbc8a3858","tid":562951,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知以前香港初一到初三警察其實有條不明文規條 就係初一到初三都唔會點抄牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95029098b32beb0b96cf2cac8bcfad979135d2d1","tid":562951,"uid":108756,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"做咩負評 我唔係撐警啲人來喎<br />\n只係想講英植時期比依家有人情味得多<br />\n同埋我無車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086358c564a5579d6b54346c38ede8b1164e5453","tid":562951,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"乜依家唔係咩"},{"pid":"2446b41ed015fa31a00f2b38eba467f591f82d13","tid":562951,"uid":2676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"呢兩年開始抄返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d931b7ef86fb50ec73381f1a82de9b36462836","tid":562951,"uid":106289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"佢地係控訴緊冇開工利是呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4f00b4c640eb20b3a5d3ba2a5156934d43e8dc","tid":562951,"uid":46431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"五十萬架私家車無九成都八成出左街啦, 周圍亂泊好難唔抄<br />\n你睇下今日幾多單炒車/ 阻巴士"},{"pid":"4c9661900be600c7f6c64e8144ff274cd8c557d2","tid":562951,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"警方指農曆新年期間照樣嚴打違泊。記者今日巡查竹園北邨一帶，該處的露天停車處，有保安在路口架起封條，只讓落客的車進入，車場內20多個車位已泊滿，更有十多輛車要泊在其中一條行車線。竹園邨一旁的盈福苑停車場亦已爆滿，停車場外有20多部車排隊等候，佔用了其中一行車線。<br />\n<br />\n以往違泊情況同樣較嚴重的竹園街市對出竹園道，記者下午巡視時就已見到警方到場執法，沿路包括雙黃線及非雙黃線位置停泊的私家車無一倖免，現場所見至少2、30多部車「中招」被抄牌。該處違泊嚴重，雙線亦單線，令道路頗擠塞。<br />\n至於黃大仙廟對出黃大仙道則有交通督導員維持秩序，即使該處的停車場外有車輛排隊進入停車場，也未有造成太大交通擠塞。<br />\n車主金女士指，過去都曾在新年期間到竹園邨拜年，曾試過被抄牌，故她盡量將車輛停泊在停車場，但停車場經常沒有車位，「試過等成兩個幾鐘先入到停車場。」今日她剛巧打算到附近購物，但見有警員抄牌即不敢久留，稍後會將私家車泊入停車場，「依家車多但停車場位又少，過年應該可以手鬆啲。」她指停車場收費亦頗貴，「我拍一日都百幾蚊，呢度（違例泊車）都係三百幾，都係多百幾蚊，又可以即刻上去（拜年），由得佢啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518776893_1b29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518776893_1b29.jpg&h=b47ab648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518776895_1903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518776895_1903.jpg&h=ea5d2064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518776904_ae6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518776904_ae6a.jpg&h=9fe9eb9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180216/large/1518776906_1226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180216%2Flarge%2F1518776906_1226.jpg&h=deccb517&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16e4897796f92a98355d097a5669e350398e06a2","tid":562951,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"抵比啦認真"},{"pid":"dfd6968a1d2a950198c2a89bc722fb5ae4f223f8","tid":562951,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"今日先見到佢地抄牌"},{"pid":"de7ebb5f103ea1523d27db90d639318e8e283a32","tid":562951,"uid":41684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"樓下抄緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84780f536943cd9d283ad97b3abe31960f4d2428","tid":562951,"uid":2080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95029098b32beb0b96cf2cac8bcfad979135d2d1","tid":562951,"uid":108756,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"做咩負評 我唔係撐警啲人來喎<br />\n只係想講英植時期比依家有人情味得多<br />\n同埋我無車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:30:25.000Z","msg":"傻系 97前有無咁撚多人亂打999報違泊，自己搵唔到位務求大家攬炒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家郁d就報，唔到場就等打包，到場唔告就疏忽職守，咁無撚計啦齊齊收利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}